police force -- which recently resolved some internal problems -- is facing a 
takeover attempt by the L.A. Police Department. Mayor Tom Bradley has ordered a 
study of the LAPD proposal, which is opposed by officials at one of the busiest 
airports in the nation. ; Photo, Sean Hector, an airport police officer, 
unsnarls traffic jam. Airport police feel threatened by the LAPD. LARRY DAVIS / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
