</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
* Michelle Gladstone has joined the Carlsbad office of Sun Harbor Realty as a 
residential agent. 
</P>
</TEXT>
