FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; WEST GERMANY -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; MILITARY 
FORCE REDUCTIONS; EUROPE -- SECURITY; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES; USSR -- 
ARMED FORCES; WEAPONS 
</P>
