</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ARMENIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; OFFICIAL VISITS; LOS ANGELES -- SCHOOLS; 
ARMENIANS -- LOS ANGELES; ARMENIA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; USSR -- 
TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; ARMENIA -- GOVERNMENT; NATIONALISM; SECESSION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
